=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Classes_FBSineN_ex2 ===

DESCRIPTION: A very_bright pure_tone sound, with square_like oscillator character around 1385 Hz, featuring punchy attack and compressed envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, filtered with resonant_steep_rolloff character, and spectrally rich.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: punchy
  brightness: very_bright
  crest_factor_db: compressed
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: pure_tone
  spectral_complexity_mean: rich
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 1384.8585
  harmonic_decay_rate: -12.3688
  harmonic_regularity: 0.9126
  pitch_clarity: 92.0662
  inharmonicity: 0.0020
  type: square_like
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -15.5943
  resonance_freq: 12424.6582

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
